name: Soul-Powered Machine
description: Instead of fighting like people do, fight like ships do. Fight like plastic toys do. Fight like you don't have a body, like you don't hate your body. Fight your way into a new body.

description: ...the crackling, broken radio's song is louder and more lovely every minute. We are our own company now.

id: #"If I could lock myself up in my memories and let my heartbeat alone take the reins, how much simpler would life be?"
